configuration.name: Script fit edgeR model and heatmap

item.itemvalue: R Script.Script fit edgeR model affected
R Script.Script fit edgeR model and heatmap

MESSAGE.value: Add FutureTable to the scope considered by ColumnRef. This makes it possible to reference columns generated by other steps (after a first run of the script).

Add support for parenthetized expressions. Add presentation for ColumnRef. Show style in FitXByY. Add intention to switch X and Y in FitXByY. Fix TrainModel to calculate predicted values on the correct platform.
Revise to use latest allogenomics tsv file.
Rename script as analysis. Try to improve scope for TableRef, not working yet.
Add plugin build script for version 1.0.0.
Include XChart and UI in the devkit. Rename to metaR. Use long name for plugin.
Rename to metaR. Fix script calculation and support virtual packages.
Add plugin description. Increase version number to 1.0.2.
Rename all languages to metaR.
Draft edgeR language. Not working yet and contrast should use column groups, not usage groups.
Add columnsWithType on GroupUsage. Start to refactor constracts to refer to levels in the factors defined in the model formula.
Add factor level mean term in group expression.
Support - operator in contrast equation.
New intention to add a group to all columns of a Table.
Generate edgeR up to the point where we estimate dispersion.
Now produce results in an R table, but not connected to concept output table yet.
Fix generation of - binary operator.
Put the output in the destination table.
